","genre_ids":[18,53,80],"popularity":3.2757,"vote_count":3616,"poster_path":"/3qnO72NHmUgs9JZXAmu4aId9QDl.jpg","release_date":"2005-09-23","vote_average":7.164,"backdrop_path":"/iZHJsUYxhjI6kbooHoQRWXv6F8E.jpg","original_title":"A History of Violence","original_language":"en"},{"id":79,"adult":false,"title":"Hero","video":false,"overview":"During China's Warring States period, a district prefect arrives at the palace of Qin Shi Huang, claiming to have killed the three assassins who had made an attempt on the king's life three years ago.","genre_ids":[18,12,28,36],"popularity":5.4979,"vote_count":2436,"poster_path":"/vxgZto2Cz7ILHAlmRXt50I2brB2.jpg","release_date":"2002-12-19","vote_average":7.508,"backdrop_path":"/jDz6RYN3nKYtlo7J9IMvGoJit7B.jpg","original_title":"英雄","original_language":"zh"},{"id":1590,"adult":false,"title":"Copying Beethoven","video":false,"overview":"A fictionalised exploration of Beethoven's life in his final days working on his Ninth Symphony. It is 1824. Beethoven is racing to finish his new symphony. However, it has been years since his last success and he is plagued by deafness, loneliness and personal trauma. A copyist is urgently needed to help the composer. A fictional character is introduced in the form of a young conservatory student and aspiring composer named Anna Holtz. The mercurial Beethoven is skeptical that a woman might become involved in his masterpiece but slowly comes to trust in Anna's assistance and in the end becomes quite fond of her. By the time the piece is performed, her presence in his life is an absolute necessity. Her deep understanding of his work is such that she even corrects mistakes he has made, while her passionate personality opens a door into his private world.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.7797,"vote_count":180,"poster_path":"/xplAbPXhZF9B3H4OnhjQsEKUESe.jpg","release_date":"2006-09-10","vote_average":6.425,"backdrop_path":"/7b3cLZjiOIR8pqjnF2g2GkBwcZ4.jpg","original_title":"Copying Beethoven","original_language":"en"},{"id":1598,"adult":false,"title":"Cape Fear","video":false,"overview":"Sam Bowden is a small-town corporate attorney. Max Cady is a tattooed, cigar-smoking, Bible-quoting, psychotic rapist. What do they have in common? 14 years ago, Sam was a public defender assigned to Max Cady's rape trial, and he made a serious error: he hid a document from his illiterate client that could have gotten him acquitted. Now, the cagey Cady has been released, and he intends to teach Sam Bowden and his family a thing or two about loss.","genre_ids":[18,80,53],"popularity":3.6632,"vote_count":3776,"poster_path":"/ws4mrtndzgSH5QGCamOFAgilr2R.jpg","release_date":"1991-11-13","vote_average":7.255,"backdrop_path":"/ntgpger7OwFNlEldxuvvFHDKzjW.jpg","original_title":"Cape Fear","original_language":"en"},{"id":1577,"adult":false,"title":"Resident Evil: Apocalypse","video":false,"overview":"As the city is locked down under quarantine, Alice finds out that the people that died from the previous incident at the Umbrella Corporation have turned into zombies. She then joins a small band of elite soldiers, who are enlisted to rescue the missing daughter of the creator of the mutating T-virus.  Once lack of luck and resources happen, they begin to wage an exhilarating battle to survive and escape before the Umbrella Corporation erases its experiment from the face of the earth.","genre_ids":[27,28,878],"popularity":3.2609,"vote_count":4639,"poster_path":"/way9dOm4dM2sm9UMcu2PEXMTX0q.jpg","release_date":"2004-09-10","vote_average":6.354,"backdrop_path":"/5PJP3NaiH9ZJRzrEHLeqSY5rNxb.jpg","original_title":"Resident Evil: Apocalypse","original_language":"en"},{"id":1585,"adult":false,"title":"It's a Wonderful Life","video":false,"overview":"George Bailey has spent his entire life giving to the people of Bedford Falls.  All that prevents rich skinflint Mr. Potter from taking over the entire town is George's modest building and loan company.  But on Christmas Eve the business's $8,000 is lost and George's troubles begin.","genre_ids":[18,10751,14],"popularity":7.0259,"vote_count":4792,"poster_path":"/mV3VcmMJN6Zwahj42dy9WwPUyRI.jpg","release_date":"1946-12-20","vote_average":8.276,"backdrop_path":"/3q35nBLCIdEbxYfsr7D5ocYQXKz.jpg","original_title":"It's a Wonderful Life","original_language":"en"},{"id":273248,"adult":false,"title":"The Hateful Eight","video":false,"overview":"Bounty hunters seek shelter from a raging blizzard and get caught up in a plot of betrayal and deception.","genre_ids":[18,9648,37],"popularity":9.3547,"vote_count":15035,"poster_path":"/jIywvdPjia2t3eKYbjVTcwBQlG8.jpg","release_date":"2015-12-25","vote_average":7.8,"backdrop_path":"/7g1zO5t0bd27Iqn5ZUDJmksOGPJ.jpg","original_title":"The Hateful Eight","original_language":"en"},{"id":273284,"adult":false,"title":"WWE Money in the Bank 2014","video":true,"overview":"Money in the Bank was a professional wrestling pay-per-view (PPV) event and WWE Network event produced by WWE. It took place on June 29, 2014 at the TD Garden in Boston, Massachusetts. It was the fifth annual Money in the Bank event.","genre_ids":[28,18],"popularity":0.272,"vote_count":17,"poster_path":"/4HqyzOYtcjwYIfcUh1Ezz4gG3Zb.jpg","release_date":"2014-06-29","vote_average":7.6,"backdrop_path":"/y1BpSl5giARChA3G7FPjGpO4YEI.jpg","original_title":"WWE Money in the Bank 2014","original_language":"en"},{"id":1727,"adult":false,"title":"Bird on a Wire","video":false,"overview":"An FBI informant has kept his new identity secret for 15 years. Now an old flame has recognised him, and the bad guys are back for revenge.","genre_ids":[28,12,35,10749],"popularity":2.2034,"vote_count":1014,"poster_path":"/liMWv3o05MbXV0QoDdFNsincUxa.jpg","release_date":"1990-05-18","vote_average":6.224,"backdrop_path":"/JWFDfwAYg8xMKwYKMv3oOqXc79.jpg","original_title":"Bird on a Wire","original_language":"en"},{"id":1729,"adult":false,"title":"The Forbidden Kingdom","video":false,"overview":"An American teenager who is obsessed with Hong Kong cinema and kung-fu classics makes an extraordinary discovery in a Chinatown pawnshop: the legendary stick weapon of the Chinese sage and warrior, the Monkey King. With the lost relic in hand, the teenager unexpectedly finds himself travelling back to ancient China to join a crew of warriors from martial arts lore on a dangerous quest to free the imprisoned Monkey King.","genre_ids":[28,12,14],"popularity":3.493,"vote_count":1865,"poster_path":"/z8chF1Z7hyuSVqLYTgElkQZh2VB.jpg","release_date":"2008-04-17","vote_average":6.623,"backdrop_path":"/9a59H9qoAzMcj1NWurMgvg9iLaT.jpg","original_title":"The Forbidden Kingdom","original_language":"en"},{"id":1808,"adult":false,"title":"Velvet Goldmine","video":false,"overview":"Almost a decade since larger-than-life glam-rock enigma Brian Slade disappeared from public eye, an investigative journalist is on assignment to uncover the truth behind his former idol.","genre_ids":[18,10402],"popularity":1.4349,"vote_count":534,"poster_path":"/bsuSac0PldPFcOtR1Vioe7VBF4l.jpg","release_date":"1998-08-28","vote_average":6.875,"backdrop_path":"/zUs2GW4rPSIsfzBp0GtXaQR2mqk.jpg","original_title":"Velvet Goldmine","original_language":"en"},{"id":1885,"adult":false,"title":"The Karate Kid","video":false,"overview":"New Jersey teen Daniel LaRusso moves to Los Angeles with his mother, and soon strikes up a relationship with Ali. He quickly finds himself the target of bullying by a group of thugs, led by Ali's ex-boyfriend Johnny, who study karate at the Cobra Kai dojo under ruthless sensei John Kreese. Fortunately, Daniel befriends Mr. Miyagi, an unassuming repairman who just happens to be a martial arts master himself. Miyagi takes Daniel under his wing, training him in a more compassionate form of karate for self-defense and, later, preparing him to compete against the brutal Cobra Kai.","genre_ids":[28,12,18,10751],"popularity":6.2323,"vote_count":4600,"poster_path":"/1mp4ViklKvA0WXXsNvNx0RBuiit.jpg","release_date":"1984-06-22","vote_average":7.2,"backdrop_path":"/j1xaeJZOEOiVBD1rk3dg4YaAk23.jpg","original_title":"The Karate Kid","original_language":"en"},{"id":1923,"adult":false,"title":"Twin Peaks: Fire Walk with Me","video":false,"overview":"In the questionable town of Deer Meadow, Washington, FBI Agent Desmond inexplicably disappears while hunting for the man who murdered a teen girl. The killer is never apprehended, and, after experiencing dark visions and supernatural encounters, Agent Dale Cooper chillingly predicts that the culprit will claim another life. Meanwhile, in the more cozy town of Twin Peaks, hedonistic beauty Laura Palmer hangs with lowlifes and seems destined for a grisly fate.","genre_ids":[18,9648,27],"popularity":6.2987,"vote_count":2202,"poster_path":"/mxsGXqetGnirf99qapYd5MMY1VL.jpg","release_date":"1992-06-03","vote_average":7.4,"backdrop_path":"/amGU1FpELmenVvNmPShW58Orepy.jpg","original_title":"Twin Peaks: Fire Walk with Me","original_language":"en"},{"id":2004,"adult":false,"title":"Kebab Connection","video":false,"overview":"In Hamburg, Ibrahim \"Ibo\" Secmez, of Turkish descent, wants to direct the first German kung-fu movie. For now, he makes commercials for his uncle's kebab restaurant. Titzie, an aspiring actress and Ibo's German girlfriend, finds she's pregnant. Ibo is uncertain about fatherhood - compounded by his father's disowning him for getting a German girl pregnant - so Titzie sends him packing. He makes attempts at getting it right, but as the birth approaches, he's still not ready. In the background are three thugs in search of good tripe soup and a Capulet-Montegue feud between the kebab joint and a Greek taverna across the street. Can Ibo be the glove upon that hand?","genre_ids":[35,28,10749],"popularity":0.3822,"vote_count":71,"poster_path":"/jNHsAVtJEzAGQJnv3AGagBSAFLu.jpg","release_date":"2004-04-21","vote_average":6.655,"backdrop_path":"/s2XyJwZ2nmtbCT8ZE3oPlm0yq1j.jpg","original_title":"Kebab Connection","original_language":"de"},{"id":1061536,"adult":false,"title":"Detective Chen","video":false,"overview":"A rookie Shanghai police captain disguises himself as a student to investigate a murder at a local high school. However, he hates studying, Therefore he must juggle homework and solving the crime case.","genre_ids":[28,80,35,9648],"popularity":0.425,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/rRFzMI88IqxojpTFieneCPiqglg.jpg","release_date":"2022-12-15","vote_average":3.3,"backdrop_path":"/tmOoETLwjrUnb1EhvZ4LktD4Y3j.jpg","original_title":"逃学神探","original_language":"zh"},{"id":2046,"adult":false,"title":"The Gift","video":false,"overview":"Annie Wilson, young widow and mother of three, makes her living foretelling others' futures⁠—though her own has become cloudier than even she can see. Threatened by a client's violent husband and plagued by visions of a missing local woman, Annie finds herself pulled into a thicket of lies and deception in which her extraordinary gift may ultimately get her killed.","genre_ids":[27,18,53,9648],"popularity":2.6736,"vote_count":1348,"poster_path":"/c9mrttn6IpvO5dymlxqCDKklMYd.jpg","release_date":"2000-12-22","vote_average":6.471,"backdrop_path":"/qVUbWtSmxtJ9iDvCrQZaiGikbTe.jpg","original_title":"The Gift","original_language":"en"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt6917210","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":"Q55606088","instagram_id":"buffaloboys.movie","metacritic_id":"movie/buffalo-boys","rotten_tomatoes_id":"m/buffalo_boys_2019"},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":"buffaloboys.movie"},"gdvg_id":148319,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_accolades":null,"release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"CA","release_dates":[{"note":"Fantasia International Film Festival","type":1,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2018-07-14T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"18A"}]},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","release_dates":[{"note":"","typ